Happy Beautiful Clients | Whenever I do a makeup job for one of my clients, I like to remind them that beauty not only comes from using great products but is #connectedbeauty from also maintaining a healthy body and mind. They get the full luxe treatment, from great skincare products from @muradskincareaus; coconut water to make sure they are hydrated; to soothing music and scented candles to calm their minds (and help with their mental health). They have also been so happy that I've given them extra pampering when I use #muradskincareaus hydro-Dynamic Quenching Essence and the super innovative Eye Lift Firming Treatment while I do their eyemakeup. No worries about fallout as it acts as a shadow shield and my clients leave looking and feeling happy which makes me happy! 
Murad is now available in Australia online at www.murad.com.au; select salons and at @sephoraus

It's a beautiful life | The path to great skin is all about #connectedbeauty. @muradskincareaus is finally here in Australia! I love Dr Murad's philosophy about the secret to great health. Just 4 things to remember. Nourish your skin with Murad's skincare. 'Eat' your water by consuming lots of water-rich fruits and drinking plenty of water; make sure you get lots of exercise to awaken your body; and finally relax your mind, turn off that phone/computer/iPad and just smell the roses. My current favourite Murad products which both have SPF15 PA++ are the Invisiblur Perfecting Shield and my holy grail Oil-Control Mattifier (keeps my blemishes in check and which I used to have to purchase from the USA). Both work great as a makeup primer plus my husband loves them too! You can now buy Murad at www.murad.com.au; selected salons and Sephora!
